Package: searchpath
Type: Package
Title: Add Packages to the Search Path
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Bill Venables
Maintainer: Bill Venables <Bill.Venables@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: pingr, utils
Description: Facilitate the addition of multiple packages
  to the search path, installing any which are necessary on
  the fly.  Removes the need for multiple library() calls.
